data.description: This 4 bedroom 2.5 bath Colonial, has been upgraded with you in mind.  Its features include: granite counter tops, newer ceramic floors in the foyer, dining room, eat in kitchen, powder room and laundry room.  A granite counter top Island with enough space for all your food preparations, stainless steel appliances,  washer, dryer, contemporary cabinets, recessed lights, ceiling fans, and freshly painted walls.  But wait, it doesn't end there.  The hot water heater, electrical panel,  bathrooms, bedrooms with laminate flooring, fresh paint, and a newer hallway light have also been upgraded.   Oh no! there's nothing left for you to do.  I guess you have to just move in, and enjoy the evenings on the patio.  See you soon.
